## 3. 输入验证与数据安全

### 3.1 SQL 注入防护

```java
// ✅ Good: 使用 Lambda QueryWrapper（自动参数化）
List<Transaction> list = transactionMapper.selectList(
    new LambdaQueryWrapper<Transaction>()
        .eq(Transaction::getUserId, userId)
        .like(Transaction::getRemark, keyword)
);

// ✅ Good: 使用 DTO 对象传参 + script 标签
@Select("<script>" +
    "SELECT * FROM t_transaction " +
    "WHERE user_id = #{dto.userId} " +
    "<if test='dto.categoryId != null'>AND category_id = #{dto.categoryId}</if>" +
    "</script>")
List<Transaction> search(@Param("dto") TransactionQueryDTO dto);

// ❌ Bad: 字符串拼接
@Select("SELECT * FROM t_transaction WHERE id = " + id)
```

### 3.2 XSS 防护

```java
// ✅ Good: 使用 OWASP Java Encoder
import org.owasp.encoder.Encode;
model.addAttribute("userInput", Encode.forHtmlContent(userInput));

// ✅ Good: 富文本使用 jsoup 净化
import org.jsoup.Jsoup;
import org.jsoup.safety.Safelist;
public String sanitizeHtml(String dirtyHtml) {
    return Jsoup.clean(dirtyHtml, Safelist.relaxed()
        .removeTags("script", "iframe", "object", "embed", "link", "style")
        .removeAttributes(":all", "onclick", "onload", "onerror"));
}
```

### 3.3 敏感数据保护

```java
// ✅ Good: 统一响应包装，不暴露内部实现细节
@ExceptionHandler(BusinessException.class)
public Result<Void> handleBusinessException(BusinessException e) {
    log.error("业务异常: userId={}, code={}", getCurrentUserId(), e.getCode(), e);
    return Result.error(e.getCode(), e.getUserMessage());
}

@ExceptionHandler(Exception.class)
public Result<Void> handleGenericException(Exception e) {
    log.error("系统异常", e);
    // ❌ Bad: return Result.error(e.getMessage()) — 暴露堆栈信息！
    return Result.error("系统繁忙，请稍后再试");
}

// ✅ Good: 敏感字段使用 @JsonIgnore
@JsonIgnore
private String password;

// ✅ Good: 数据脱敏序列化
@JsonSerialize(using = DesensitizeSerializer.class)
private String phone;  // 输出: 138****5678
```

